{"tid":136430,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"（唉）平時見開既貓貓死左………","createTime":"2017-02-27T05:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T13:39:34.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0681f4932f18ff8011ed8cbdbf565ccb695cf37","tid":136430,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:06:16.000Z","msg":"隻喵四腳踏雪，平時都會走黎我屋前度晒下太陽，訓下覺<br />\n<br />\n不過勁怕人，我一行出去就會極速走。<br />\n<br />\n年年呢個時候晚晚都會係屋頂叫春。<br />\n<br />\n今朝出門見到佢伏屍係隔離屋大閘入面。應該係琴晚佢走左入去人地度，畀隔離屋隻狗咬死。<br />\n<br />\n唉。<br />\n<br />\n隔離屋未返黎，我送唔到佢最後一程。唯有返轉頭拎一束香裝畀佢。希望佢下世過得幸福。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢個係大自然，但我都sad到而家。"},{"pid":"fb79dff79e0354789fdb01f525f54c9cf78884d5","tid":136430,"uid":55016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"貓貓。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1466ae01f65cd2a0c4d0151d7a31830780a52562","tid":136430,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21739e73d94a021f94ffe0d644a5fdbda883729","tid":136430,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:26:20.000Z","msg":"貓都恰得狗多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f8df7c9500ffdc78484500aa664b3db7724f8d","tid":136430,"uid":39717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:36:06.000Z","msg":"其實貓身手好，又敏捷，健康嘅情況底下好少比狗咬死。<br />\n可能佢本身已經病病地，所以比隻狗有機可乘&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5608598f769a4f71ce5225f5a3b0dcf7313e3ab5","tid":136430,"uid":45344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"